  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age &gt; 18 years

          -  accepted to participate

          -  Patients followed in vascular medicine and entrusted to the home medical care for the
             bandages of chronic wounds with apathetic ulcers, not presenting of granulation tissue
             on their surface

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  infected ulcers

          -  necrosed ulcers

          -  Arterial ulcers requiring a revascularisation.

          -  Ulcers whose surface is superior in 10x10 cm.
      </textblock>
